title: Over/Under: 2017 rookie class predictions
itunes:title: Over/Under: 2017 rookie class predictions
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Colleen Wolfe, & Gregg Rosenthal – recap all the latest news from Around the NFL including Jay Cutler taking a job in the broadcast booth with Fox, and Saints center Max Unger out 5 months after undergoing foot surgery. Then the heroes break down expectations for the 2017 rookie class in a friendly game of over/under. Plus...we dip into the mailbag and answer some of the most pressing questions from you, the fans!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
